# Only input.env + golden-*.txt are committed. Everything the builder
# materializes at (re)build time — the seeded cache.db (+ WAL/SHM sidecars),
# the fake HOME's .local data dir, and the real per-project .git roots used to
# exercise the git-root walk in _resolve_project_key — is regenerated into a
# scratch dir by bin/cctally-daily-instances-test / bin/cctally-reconcile-test
# and must never land in the tree (would leak absolute paths + dirty on every
# rebuild). Goldens show only project LABELS, so they stay location-stable.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*/.local/
*/work/
*/personal/
*/repos/
